{"id":"f64dafdb-e6d4-4eba-bab8-587def144a90","name":"Kerry Eurodyne ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/W0dgvMFM23iOMRHguPBq3.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3SUsQNuENlIKwsDb3Wk2Q.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6Z43r3F2_kaFTQ2MWKQOu.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong>“ᴀᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ᴇɴᴅ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ ᴡɪᴛʜ ʏᴏᴜ”</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ᴜꜱᴇʀ=ᴠ • ᴋᴇʀʀʏ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✨<strong>[ᴀɴᴏɴ ʙᴏᴛ ʀᴇQᴜᴇꜱᴛ]</strong>✨</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hLUcW0Pu_BmRedLBZ0kE-.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 182, 182);\">“𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐄𝐍𝐃” • 𝐉𝐏𝐎𝐋𝐍𝐃</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 141, 145);\"><strong>⇄ ◁◁ I I ▷▷ ↻</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 141, 145);\"><strong>⁰⁰ ²⁵ ━━●━━━━━━━━ ⁰² ⁰⁸</strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/68YAU_EMShlTTgdaPshWn.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113);\"><strong>Images:</strong> <em>My in-game screenshots. Do not repost.</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vgemc7SvLeoa_6y9bWXlG.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Frentry.org%2Fabsolutetrash-likes-templates%23persona-templates\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>ʜᴇʀᴇ’ꜱ ᴀ ɢᴜɪᴅᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴄʀᴇᴀᴛɪɴɢ ɢᴏᴏᴅ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀs.</strong></span></a></p><hr><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/2KVfllH84xcoplnnUPcmv.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong>ᴅᴇᴇᴘꜱᴇᴇᴋ:</strong> ᴛʀʏ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fcheesey-wizards-organization.gitbook.io%2Fmasterlist%2Fprompts-and-troubleshooting%2Fmy-prompts\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>ᴘʀᴏᴍᴘᴛ ʙʏ ꜱᴀᴛᴜʀɴɪɴᴇꜱ//ᴄʜᴇᴇꜱᴇ</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"> </span>ᴀɴᴅ ᴘʀᴀʏ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ᴀɪ ɢᴏᴅꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>ꜰᴏʀ ᴊʟʟᴍ &amp; ᴘʀᴏxɪᴇꜱ:</strong> <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Frentry.org%2Fkolach3prompts%23full-prompt\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 210, 212);\"><strong>ᴋᴏʟᴀᴄʜ3’ꜱ ᴀᴅᴠᴀɴᴄᴇᴅ ᴘʀᴏᴍᴘᴛ</strong></span></a>.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>/ᐠ • ˕ •マ ?</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/33MsXI01Y85Ja8SAcdxID.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><ul><li><p><strong>ᴄᴡ:</strong> ɪᴛ’ꜱ ᴀ ᴄʏʙᴇʀᴘᴜɴᴋ ʙᴏᴛ ꜱᴏ, ʏᴇᴀʜ. 🤷🏼‍♀️ ᴜɴᴅᴇʀʟʏɪɴɢ ᴅᴀʀᴋ ᴛʜᴇᴍᴇꜱ ᴡɪʟʟ ʙᴇ ᴛʜᴇʀᴇ.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>ʟᴏʀᴇ: </strong>ʜᴇ’ꜱ ʙᴇᴇɴ ꜰᴇᴅ ʜɪꜱ ʙᴀᴄᴋꜱᴛᴏʀʏ. ʜɪꜱ ʀᴇʟᴀᴛɪᴏɴꜱʜɪᴘ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴠ ᴀɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴛʀᴀɪɴᴇᴅ ᴏɴᴇ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴊᴏʜɴɴʏ.</p></li><li><p><strong>ᴋɪɴᴋꜱ:</strong> ᴛʜᴇʀᴇ ᴀʀᴇ <strong>ɴᴏ ꜱᴘᴇᴄɪꜰɪᴄ ᴋɪɴᴋꜱ</strong> ʙᴀᴋᴇᴅ ɪɴᴛᴏ ᴛʜɪꜱ ʙᴏᴛ, ᴏᴛʜᴇʀᴡɪꜱᴇ ɪ ᴡᴏᴜʟᴅ <strong>ᴀʙꜱᴏʟᴜᴛᴇʟʏ</strong> ᴡᴀʀɴ ʏᴏᴜ ʙᴇᴄᴀᴜꜱᴇ ɪ ᴄʜᴏᴏꜱᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴋᴇᴇᴘ ᴄʜᴀʀ ᴅᴇꜰ ʜɪᴅᴅᴇɴ. ɪ ᴋɴᴏᴡ ꜱᴏᴍᴇ ᴘᴇᴏᴘʟᴇ ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ ʟɪᴋᴇ ᴛʜᴀᴛ, ʙᴜᴛ ɪᴛ’ꜱ ᴍʏ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟ ᴘʀᴇꜰᴇʀᴇɴᴄᴇ. ꜱᴏᴡʏ 🥺</p></li><li><p><strong>ᴘʀᴏxʏ ᴜꜱᴇʀꜱ:</strong> ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴜꜱᴇ <strong>ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ</strong> ᴏʀ <strong>ᴄʟᴀᴜᴅᴇ</strong>, ꜱᴏ ɪ ᴄᴀɴ’ᴛ ꜱᴘᴇᴀᴋ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜᴏꜱᴇ. ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏ</strong> ᴜꜱᴇ <strong>ᴅᴇᴇᴘꜱᴇᴇᴋ</strong>. <strong>ᴛᴇᴍᴘᴇʀᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ</strong> ɪꜱ ɪᴍᴘᴏʀᴛᴀɴᴛ ᴛᴏᴏ.</p></li><li><p><strong>ɪꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ꜱᴛᴀʀᴛꜱ ꜱᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ꜰᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ,</strong> ɪᴛ’ꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ. ʀᴇʀᴏʟʟ, ᴏʀ ᴇᴅɪᴛ. <strong>ɪꜰ ᴅᴇᴇᴘꜱᴇᴇᴋ ɪꜱ ᴛᴀʟᴋɪɴɢ ꜰᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ</strong> (ᴀ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴏɴ ᴘʀᴏʙʟᴇᴍ) ʜᴀᴠɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ᴀᴅᴠᴀɴᴄᴇᴅ ᴘʀᴏᴍᴘᴛ ɪ ʟɪɴᴋᴇᴅ ᴀʙᴏᴠᴇ ᴄᴜᴛꜱ ᴅᴏᴡɴ ᴏɴ ᴛʜᴀᴛ.</p></li></ul><hr><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AcIVzUeaC1uq40MtxzbPQ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"backgr","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"iigFmzsfqoSvXzQea25Ek.webp","creator":"deathintheafternoon","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst"],"chats":746,"messages":28087,"created_at":"2025-08-24T03:08:26.324108+00:00"}